How to purchase tickets for Baozi & Hana Singapore Fan Meeting 2017[Step 1]Ticketing sales will open for each session at respective timeslots stated below.The registration link will only be posted on the event page when sales start.Fan meeting Session ONE (CASUAL): 20 May, 10am-12.30pmTicketing sales open: 8 April (Sat), 12pm ~ 3pmFan meeting Session TWO (COSPLAY): 20 May, 2pm-4.30pmTicketing sales open: 8 April (Sat), 4pm ~ 7pm[Step 2]After clicking onto the registration link on the event page, you will be directed to theregistration form Section 1: Terms & ConditionsPlease read carefully before proceeding, and tick agree upon acceptance of the terms &ConditionsSection 2: Registration DetailsPlease fill in details in the form accordingly.- Do note only 2 tickets per session is allowed.- Please fill in your real name as per identity card, as it will be used for verification duringregistration on the actual day of fan meeting[Step 3]You will get an e-mail reply with payment instructions (1st email) within the next hour, only if you have successfully secured a slot with us.Please make payment within 3 hours of receiving the email. Failure to do so, your registration slot will be forfeited and released to others.For those who do not receive any emails, please wait to see if a slot has opened up!Payment methods:ATM / Bank transfer (Our banks are: POSB/DBS)PayPal for Overseas fans. Additional PayPal charge will be incurred so ONE ticket is S$23.50, TWO tickets will be $46.50 (This extra charge is collected by PayPal, not us!)[Step 4]Make payment within the time-frame allocated.If you do not make payment within the time-frame, your registration slot will be given to someone else.[Step 5]Once we confirmed your payment, we will send an email to you to inform successful ticketpurchase (2nd email).Another separate email (3rd email) will be sent to you on the seat number allocated within24 hours of ticket purchase.In summary, you will receive 3 emails upon successful ticket purchase:1) 1st email: registration slot & payment instructions2) 2nd email: confirmation of purchase3) 3rd email: seat allocation

Hi everyone! Here's the first wave of publicity for the long-awaited SGFM2.0!

We are glad to organise this event in collaboration with SG Fanclub~ The date is set on 20 May, and this is the only chance for us to meet everyone in first half of this year, hope everyone can support usğŸ’ªğŸ’ª Similar to last year, the FM will be split into morning session (Casual) and afternoon session (Cosplay, we will cos as Victor and Yuriâ˜º)! Since this is our second time organising SGFM, we strive to make it better, by adding more interesting segments, more gifts and a lucky draw! (Prizes include not-for-sale items such as cushions and wall scroll posters~) In appreciation of our Singapore fans' support for so many years, the ticket price will be reduced to SGD22, while at the same time, we will add on more event gifts; besides tote bags, postcards and badges, we are considering to prepare items like keychains as event gifts~ Hope everyone will like them~ Of course, there will be new merchandise for sale at the event, which we will announce in advance~

Lastly, as the date of event is close to Hana's birthday, we will be celebrating his birthday together during the event~ Hope everyone will enjoy yourselves in this FM!

Event page & Ticketing guide:https://www.facebook.com/events/291011094653345/       

Feel free to leave your comments if you have any queries!
